item.text: The Argonaut Questionnaire Sampler is designed to show all the question types that can be used in the Argonaut Questionnaire Project: 1. boolean, 2. decimal, 3. integer, 4. dateDate, 5. dateTime, 6. timeTime, 7. string, 8. textText, 9. urlUrl, 10. choice, 11. open-choice, 12. quantity
Header Text
Check the box if the following statement is true.  The average air speed velocity of a laden European swallow is greater than a laden African swallow.
boolean
What is the average air speed velocity of a laden swallow in m/sec?
decimal
What is the average air speed velocity of a laden swallow in m/sec?
integer
If a laden swallow left Camelot on 7/5/2018 what day would it reach the Castle Anthrax?
date
If a laden swallow left Camelot on 7/5/2018 and noon when would it reach Castle Anthrax?
dateTime
If a laden swallow left Camelot at noon what time would it reach Castle Anthrax?
time
Describe how to estimate the average air speed velocity of a laden swallow in 20 words or less.
string
Describe in detal how to estimate the average air speed velocity of a laden swallow. Please cite your sources and give examples.
text
Provide a link to a video clip where the average air speed velocity of a laden swallow question is discussed.
url
What is the average air speed velocity of a laden swallow in m/sec?
choice
What is the average air speed velocity of a laden swallow in m/sec?
open-choice
What is the average air speed velocity of a laden swallow - please provide the units?
quantity
